{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "第十一回\"双刀合璧\"。谢小玉在水阁中欲自刎，丁鹏以弯刀击飞她的剑将其救下。铁燕夫人与铁燕长老联手施展\"燕子双飞、双刀合璧\"攻向丁鹏，二人双刀合璧力量倍增、浑如一体，本应无人能挡。然而丁鹏以狐族弯刀绝技反破双刀合璧，一刀削伤铁燕夫妻手腕与面颊。铁燕长老认出丁鹏的刀法源自昔年一位\"天下无双的神人\"，追问\"小楼一夜听春雨\"七字的含义，丁鹏拒答。铁燕长老亮出免死铁令要挟，南宫华树证实其效力后惊恐离去。铁燕长老以毒咒诅咒丁鹏一生悲苦，随后夫妇遁入黑暗。谢小玉向丁鹏表白仰慕与信赖，丁鹏不为所动，冷冷质问她的身份，并传话谢晓峰：十日内登门道谢道歉，否则亲赴神剑山庄挑战。宴会草草收场，柳若松以弟子身份送客，众人对其既鄙夷又暗含敬畏。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我自己要死，你为什么不让我死？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你不该死，也不能死！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我明白了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "你明白了什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "要杀谢小玉，就得先杀了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "要杀你，好像并不容易。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "大概不太容易！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你这把刀看来好像是弯的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "好像有一点弯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "近三十年来，江湖中好像从未出现过用弯刀的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "我的脖子却是直的，跟别人一样直，一样可以砍得断。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "近三十年来，江湖中也没有人看见过我们的燕子双飞，双刀合璧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "今天我是不是可以看见了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "能看到你们燕子双飞，双刀合璧的人，还能活下去的一定不太多？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "好像连一个都没有！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "可是今天我说不定会让你们破例一次。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我也希望你们能让我破例一次。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "他这把刀是弯的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "我们以前也杀过用弯刀的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "因为那些人弯刀一出手，也是直直地劈下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "只有一个人是例外。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "幸好他不是那个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_fu_ren",
      "text": "幸好他不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你用的是把弯刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "是有一点弯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不是只有一点点，你用的是把真正的弯刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "天上地下，古往今来，只有一个人能用这种刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你不是那个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "我本来就不是，我就是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你用的这把刀，也不是他的刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "这把刀本来就是我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你的这把刀上没有字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "这把刀上本来应该有字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "应该有七个字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "哪七个字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "小楼一夜听春雨。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你以前没有听过这七个字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "我听过，这是句传诵已久的名诗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你知不知道这七个字的意思。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你真的知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "这意思就是说，一个春天的晚上，有一个寂寞的人，独坐小楼，听了一夜春雨声。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不对，不对，完全不对。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "难道这句诗里面还有什么别的含意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这七个字说的是一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "——个天下无双的神人，一把天下无双的神刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不对，不对，你绝不会认得这个人的！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "你怎么知道我绝不会认得他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为他久已不在人世了，你还没有出生时，他就已不在人世了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "但是你刚才使出的那一刀，却绝对是他的刀法！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "天上地下，古往今来，只有他一个人能使出那一刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "除了他之外，好像还有一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不错，除了他之外，还有你，你究竟是什么人？怎么能使出那一刀的？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "我为什么要告诉你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你一定要告诉我，只要你告诉我，我情愿死。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "我不说也一样可以杀了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你不能杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "为什么不能？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "非但你不能杀我，普天之下，谁也不能杀我！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你看看这是什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "text": "你一定知道这是什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "speaker_name": "南宫华树",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "我知道，我当然知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "text": "你说！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "speaker_name": "南宫华树",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "这就是昔年天下英雄公认的免死铁令，是神剑山庄，和江湖中三大门帮，七大剑派，四大世家联名要求天下英雄承认的，只要有了这块免死令，无论他做了什么事，天下英雄都要免除他的一死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_fu_hu",
      "speaker_name": "孙伏虎",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "text": "这是假的，一定是假的！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "speaker_name": "南宫华树",
      "listener": "char_sun_fu_hu",
      "text": "一定不假，绝对不假。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_fu_hu",
      "speaker_name": "孙伏虎",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "text": "神剑山庄和七大剑派都是魔教的死敌，免死铁令怎么会在魔教长老的身上？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "speaker_name": "南宫华树",
      "listener": "char_sun_fu_hu",
      "text": "这其中当然有原因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_fu_hu",
      "speaker_name": "孙伏虎",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "text": "什么原因？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "speaker_name": "南宫华树",
      "listener": "char_sun_fu_hu",
      "text": "我不能说出来，可是我知道他这块铁令绝对不假。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_hua_shu",
      "speaker_name": "南宫华树",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日如果有人杀了他，就变成了神剑山庄，和三大门帮、七大剑派、四大世家的死敌，七日之内，必死无疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一生杀人无算，现在我还有一只手可以杀人，今日我若不死，这里所有的人迟早都要一个个死在我刀下，你们日日夜夜都要提心吊胆，防备我去杀你，你们在睡梦中醒来时，说不定已变成了无头的冤鬼。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你们今天绝不该叫我活着离开这里，只可惜你们偏偏又不能杀我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是我自己可以杀死我自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "只要你说出怎么能使出那一刀的，我就立刻死在这里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你说不说？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "不说！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你真的不说？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "你杀不了我的，我却随时都可以杀了你，今日我免你一死，可是以后你只要再杀一个人，我就要你的命。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "一块免死铁令，只能救你一次，我保证，下次谁也救不了你，就算是神剑山庄的谢庄主亲临，我也杀了你再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "我劝你现在最好快走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我当然要走，可是有件事我一定要告诉你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "text": "你说！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不管你那一刀是从哪里学来的，都必将为你带来无穷无尽的灾祸。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 455,
      "line_end": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "就算你能用那一刀纵横天下，但是灾祸都必将永远跟着你，日日夜夜，时时刻刻地跟着你，就算你能用那一刀换来天下无双的声名，但是你这一生都必将永远活在悲苦伤痛中，然后再伤心而死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 459,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yan_zhang_lao",
      "speaker_name": "铁燕长老",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "以天上地下所有的神魔恶鬼为证，这就是你这一生的命运！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你千万不要听他们的鬼话。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这种鬼话你连一个字都不要相信。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "鬼话有时都很灵的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "可是他们说的话我连一个字都不信，因为他们说的不是鬼话，他们是人，不是鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "就算他们真的是鬼，我相信你也不会怕他们的，我相信不管是天上，还是地下，都绝没有能让你害怕的事。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你真是谢晓峰的女儿？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是……是的！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "可是别人都说谢晓峰没有女儿。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "家父行事很少为人所知，神剑山庄更少有人前去，别的人怎么会知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "名满天下的谢家三少爷自然是不屑与俗人来往的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 535
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你可是因为我父亲没有接受你的邀请而生气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 537,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不敢当，我只是顺便发了张帖子给他，并没有想他真会来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这一点你要原谅他，多少年来，家父已经谢绝酬酢，连多少年的老朋友，他都避不见面了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 543,
      "line_end": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "可是我要来，他并没有禁止，而且还叫商震跟田一飞跟来保护我，可见他还是很尊重你这个人的！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 547,
      "line_end": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "他应该尊重，因为他派出保护你的人不但没有保护你，反而惹下了麻烦，倒是我这个他瞧不起的人，不在乎开罪两个人见人怕的魔教长老，从铁燕双飞的手中救下了他的女儿。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 551,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你不但救了我，还击败了铁燕双飞，家父知道了，也一定会认为这是很了不起的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 555,
      "line_end": 557
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "当然了，他也会很感激你的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 559,
      "line_end": 559
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "如果他很感激我，他就欠我一声道谢，如果，他认为我还算过得去，就欠我一场决斗。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 563
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你要找家父决斗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 565,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "自从谢家三少爷开始出道江湖，就一直找遍了天下的成名剑手决斗，击败了每一个对手，成就了神剑山庄的赫赫盛名。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 567,
      "line_end": 569
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "神剑山庄之名并不是从家父手中开始的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "可是你的祖先们并没有像令尊这样有名，他击败了别人才使自己成名，因此也无权拒绝别人的挑战。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 573,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "家父不会跟你决斗的，因为你不是一名剑手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 577,
      "line_end": 577
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "谢小玉",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "就算你是个很高明的剑手，他也不会跟你决斗了，自从他跟燕十三最后一次比剑后，就不再跟人决斗了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 579,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "令尊剑下杀死过很多的高手，他们并不全都是用剑的，因此他没有理由拒绝我这柄弯刀的挑战。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 605,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你回去告诉令尊，说我会等他十天，十天之内，他亲自登门道谢和道歉，我们或许可以交个朋友……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 609,
      "line_end": 609
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_yu",
      "text": "十天之后他如不来，就是有意要跟我一决，我就带了刀，找上神剑山庄去！",
      "tone": "认真",
